data.description: Assumable FHA loan at 2.25%.  Maintenance free living!  Let the HOA take care of the mowing of your entire yard, if you would like!  Neighborhood park across the street. Quartz counter tops in a beautiful, well lit kitchen. Upgraded cabinets and amazing back splash. Nice maple hardwood floors, plantation shutters throughout main floor. Master bath has separate garden tub and shower. Double vanity also. Fully fenced backyard. New trex deck. Completely finished basement with huge family room, 2 bedrooms, and a full bath.  This one will go quick!
